data.title: Lane College
data.meta_description: Discover a world-class education with Lane College. Explore programs, access information and contact the school directly
data.text:
We provide students with a profoundly transformative undergraduate education - intellectually, spiritually, and socially - and have for almost 150 years. We've nurtured business leaders and spiritual leaders, novelists and scientists, physicians and public servants, and scholars and teachers in nearly every field of endeavour.

We're one of America's oldest colleges, steeped in great social traditions. Thirty-six buildings sprawling across 55 acres create a genuinely exceptional academic and living environment.

Award-winning and accredited academic programs are offered in dozens of majors and minors - business, entrepreneurship, criminal justice, social work, health care, and more. We prepare you with the hottest in-demand career credentials.

Our campus is designed for flexibility. Giving you more options applies to everything we do - from diverse food options and tons of fitness activities to a vibrant social calendar involving over 70 Greek-letter, athletic, religious, music, and special interest group activities.
